|                   |   |                       |   |                         |
|                   |   |                       |   | **ICO enforcement       |
|                   |   |                       |   | note:** The Information |
|                   |   |                       |   | Commissioner\'s Office  |
|                   |   |                       |   | has issued enforcement  |
|                   |   |                       |   | notices against         |
|                   |   |                       |   | organisations that      |
|                   |   |                       |   | logged personal data    |
|                   |   |                       |   | inappropriately ---     |
|                   |   |                       |   | including health data   |
|                   |   |                       |   | written to application  |
|                   |   |                       |   | logs during debugging.  |
|                   |   |                       |   | Under UK GDPR, logging  |
|                   |   |                       |   | personal data requires  |
|                   |   |                       |   | a lawful basis, a       |
|                   |   |                       |   | retention limit, and    |
|                   |   |                       |   | appropriate access      |
|                   |   |                       |   | controls. Security logs |
|                   |   |                       |   | are not exempt.         |
+-------------------+---+-----------------------+---+-------------------------+

  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Juice Shop connection:** Juice Shop\'s admin panel (/api/Feedbacks,
  /api/Complaints) returns full user objects including email addresses in
  its API responses --- demonstrating both Excessive Data Exposure and
  the logging problem simultaneously. Run those requests through ZAP and
  examine what personal data would appear in an unfiltered application
  log. Then identify which fields from the left panel Juice Shop\'s own
  logging captures for those events.

  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
